<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />入春之后，<delay8 />天气渐渐暖和起来了呢！<delay frames="40" />
为了舒缓之前被冻到僵硬的身体，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想试试<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是，<delay20 />首先应该想办法
把我这怎么也消散不了的瞌睡虫<delay8 />赶跑才是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />哈～欠……<delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="5" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呼～<delay20 />好热啊！<delay frames="40" />
汗都在往下滴了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但就把这当作<delay20 />对我毅力的试练，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉突然燃起了我的斗志呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有<delay20 />好好享受秋天吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一不注意，<delay8 />秋天很快就会结束咯！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />秋天～<delay20 />真是个美好的季节！<delay frames="40" />
这个温度正好适合运动，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />更重要的是，<delay8 />秋天好吃的很多！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呜呜～<delay20 />好冷！好冷！<delay frames="30" />
这就是冬天的感觉啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说到冬天，我小时候，<delay20 />
梦想就是用雪造一个巨大的屋子，<delay8 />
然后住在里面～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呐～<tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
下次我们一起来做吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />诶？<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你放心，<delay20 />我不会强迫你一起住的！</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />刚才，那边的花儿们<delay20 />
看上去好像很高兴的样子。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是因为春天来了吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话说，<delay8 />我以前在老家的时候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />去家附近的山上<delay8 />抓了几十只蝉，<delay8 />
还拿回家向老妈炫耀。她看到后就对我大吼，<pageBreak /><10_10 /><tag a="10" b="12" /><size value="150" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />给我放回去！！<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><10_9 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />她当时生气的样子，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的超可怕～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最近，渐渐地白天开始变短了。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有时候发发呆，<delay8 />
一转眼，天就黑了。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道<delay8 />这种情况叫什么吗？<10_4 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这就是<delay20 />“迟迟白日早”啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶？<delay20 />我说错了吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这么冷的天，<delay8 />让人很想吃火锅！<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，就在几年前，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="10" />我请朋友吃过<delay8 />
我精心研制的火锅哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那家伙<delay8 />好像特别感动，<delay20 />
还特意为我的火锅起了名字，<10_4 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就叫<delay20 />“暗黑火锅”！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="10" arg="0x65 0x65 0x65 0x65 0x66 0x66" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="10" arg="0x67 0x67 0x67 0x67 0x67 0x68" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="0" arg="0x69 0x6a" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="8" arg="0x6b 0x6b 0x6c 0x6c 0x6c 0x6c 0x6b" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />气温已经回暖了！<delay frames="40" />
植物和虫子们都从地里钻出来了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />给人感觉<delay8 />生机勃勃的呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次看到这样的场景，<delay8 />都想对它们说一句<delay20 />
“早上好”<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂！<delay20 />有什么问题吗？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为什么<delay8 />一脸惊讶的表情？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个时期，<delay8 />一到夜里<delay20 />
就会突然降温，<delay8 />要注意保暖哦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果因为白天暖和而忽视了夜间的保暖<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Sneezing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><10_10 /><delay frames="16" /><size value="150" />阿嚏！！<size value="100" /><delay20 /><10_9 /><pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就会像这样！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也要小心，<delay8 />
不要<delay20 />感冒咯！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一到夏天，<delay20 />大家总是叫着“好热！好热！”。<delay frames="30" />
我觉得这样只会让人感觉更热吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然如此，<delay20 />那是不是只要喊“好冷”，<delay20 />
就会感觉凉快了呢？<delay frames="30" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这当然<delay20 />不可能啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算太阳下山了还是这么热！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像这样难以入眠的夜晚，<delay8 />最适合熬夜了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />到了晚上
还这么热的话<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />莫非这里就是<delay8 />传说中的“热岛”？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
说到秋天，你会想到什么呢？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我首先想到的绝对是“运动之秋”！<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />运动完以后吃的饭，是平时无法比拟的！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />倒应该是<delay8 />“食欲之秋”更合适！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay20 />
说到秋天，你会想到什么？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得，<delay8 />首先想到的一定是“艺术之秋”！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想象一下，<delay8 />看到画着水果的画作，<delay20 />
就会忍不住肚子饿呢～<delay frames="50" />啊！<delay frames="30" />这么一想，<delay8 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像“食欲之秋”更贴切吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个时期，<delay8 />就连空气都很寒冷，<delay20 />
所以脸经常会觉得痛呢！<pageBreak />每次打完架以后，<delay8 />被风一吹，<delay20 />
感觉要比以往痛上好几倍<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />这都是以前的事了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次下雪<delay8 />我都会很兴奋，<delay20 />
一不小心甚至会把天气的寒冷给忘了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想到以前，<delay8 />我和老家的朋友们<delay20 />
会因为下雪而开心地到处跑～<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过也是，<delay20 />那样运动<delay8 />也就不觉得冷了吧。</message>
</msbt>